{#def preset, selected=False, extra="" #}
{#
  Selectable "where to run" card for the create page -- the two compute
  presets (Imbue Cloud / local) compose from this. Renders a
  ``<button type="button">`` with ``role="radio"``; selection is driven by
  ``aria-checked`` (the create page's inline JS flips it), exactly like the
  ColorSwatch picker. The visual state is pure Tailwind:

    - default: a 1px dashed neutral outline (``outline-1 outline-dashed
      outline-strong``);
    - selected: a 2px solid accent (blue) outline (no fill tint), via the
      ``aria-checked:`` variants (so the JS only toggles the attribute, no
      class bookkeeping);
    - hover: lifts up 1px (``-translate-y-px``) with ``shadow-raised``;
      pressing settles it back down (``active:translate-y-0``) and scales to
      0.99 for a tactile click.

  The edge is an ``outline`` (not a ``border``): outlines paint outside the box
  and never take up layout space, so growing 1px -> 2px between states never
  shifts the card or its contents. ``transition-all`` eases every change -- the
  outline width/color, the hover lift, and the press scale all animate (the
  dashed -> solid style flip snaps, as outline-style isn't animatable). Tailwind
  v4 maps ``translate``/``scale`` to the standalone CSS properties, so the hover
  lift and press scale compose without fighting over ``transform``; ``active:``
  ordering wins over ``hover:``, so a press settles the lift back to 0 while
  shrinking. The caller supplies the title / badge / feature list as the
  component body.

  Props:
    preset    the ``data-preset`` value (``"remote"`` / ``"local"``); the
              page JS reads it to apply that preset's provider defaults.
    selected  initial ``aria-checked`` state (one card per radiogroup).
    extra     parent-owned sizing (e.g. ``flex-1``); the component root
              carries no outer positioning of its own.

  Any other HTML attribute (id=, data-*, aria-label=) flows through via
  JinjaX's ``attrs`` passthrough.
#}
{%- set _base = "flex flex-col gap-2 p-4 text-left cursor-pointer rounded-lg bg-surface-primary outline-1 outline-dashed outline-strong transition-all duration-150 ease-out hover:-translate-y-px hover:shadow-raised active:translate-y-0 active:scale-[0.99] aria-checked:outline-2 aria-checked:outline-solid aria-checked:outline-accent" -%}
<button {{ attrs.render(
  type="button",
  role="radio",
  classes=_base ~ " " ~ extra,
  **{"data-preset": preset, "aria-checked": "true" if selected else "false"},
) }}>{{ content }}</button>
